{
  "texts": [
    "There was a substantial difference in cost between GPT-4 and GPT-3.5, as shown in Table 4, due to the increase in cost per 1000 tokens for notes for GPT-4 (0.06) compared with GPT-3.5 (0.003).",
    "The output cost also increased from 0.004 per 1000 tokens for GPT-3.5 to 0.12 for GPT-4.",
    "Interestingly, the prompt (1778.39 USD for GPT-4) cost more than the total for all the notes (701.72 USD for GPT-4), and this was the case for GPT-3.5 as well.",
    "This is because the prompt had to be included as part of each note.",
    "Because the prompt was long (1,182 tokens), this increased the cost substantially."
  ]
}